Unknown gunmen have killed the chairman of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) in Ward 4 (Olomu Ward 1), Ughelli South council area of Delta state, Paul Onomuakpokpo. The victim was attacked at about 7 pm on Wednesday night, along Ogoni road, near the palace of Ohworode of Olomu Kingdom. Onomuakpokpo was leaving the building site where he went to supply sand when the gunmen in a White Toyota Camry opened fire on him. The Delta State police command has confirmed his killing. Details soon. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .